Revision history for Perl distribution CPAN-Testers-Data-Uploads-Mailer

0.05    2013-05-12
        - CHANGES => Changes.
        - change file dates changed to meet W3CDTF standards.
        - added LICENSE file.
        - test suite updated.
        - added test script for help().

0.04    2012-06-24
        - spelling fixes. (thanks to Florian Schlichting & Gregor Herrmann).
        - META tests no longer require specific versions.
        - added minimum perl version (5.006).
        - reworked Makefile.PL for clarity.
        - slimmed down sample file.

0.03    2010-08-12
        - added META.json to the package files.
        - fix to headers in mail template.

0.02    2010-02-06
        - documentation updates.
        - fixed repository and bugtracker links in META.yml.
        - refined parsing of command line and argument options.
        - refined filters for bad uploads.
        - added more tests & samples.
        - reworked mail template to include headers.
        - template variables reworked in code.
        - include other failed parses for admins only.

0.01    2010-01-29
        - initial release
